{"tid":1126413,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"講劇透死全家既人，一聽就知係電影門外漢","createTime":"2019-04-26T11:11:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-26T11:38:41.000Z","uid":111512,"like":4,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"03748c4d512fd5ddc5bc06d6ddc0307769789988","tid":1126413,"uid":111512,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-26T11:11:22.000Z","msg":"講真<br />\n呢排啲人關口埋口都話劇透死全家，接受唔到人劇透<br />\n有啲仲為左咁同朋友/家人/伴侶鬧交打交<br />\n話咩想有更好既觀看體驗/尊重套戲<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">聽到呢啲我真係起曬雞皮</span><br />\n<br />\n因為佢地大多都係人講佢又講，講到好爽咁<br />\n小部分就劇情撚，睇戲淨係睇劇情<br />\n<br />\n前者就屌黎都曬氣<br />\n<br />\n後者個啲，我想同你講<br />\n欣賞電影，唔係得一個角度<br />\n（雖然復4係劇情方面既10年鋪排的確出色）<br />\n但令到班撚樣講吓講吓好似好撚型咁真係好肉酸<br />\n學吓欣賞電影既唔同方面<br />\n例如拍攝分鏡，角色描寫刻劃，科幻特技，對白設計，題材選用，（諗到再講）<br />\n淨係睇劇情，根本只係比睇靚仔靚女既白痴韓劇撚高級少少<br />\n<br />\n所以，希望睇左復4而又識欣賞電影既你，快啲係你既社交平台到劇透，教育吓呢班人<br />\n如果佢屌鳩你<br />\n<br />\n你就大大聲同佢講<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">對唔到囉</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb90e36e68ad18da26c41af6b188b36aac19ef5f","tid":1126413,"uid":111512,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-26T11:14:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"827a75e82b125139c5e53a0d7135e86cc5ad72d0","tid":1126413,"uid":151865,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-26T11:15:09.000Z","msg":"做乜撚野"},{"pid":"65f38064956c19144404d534f